import { MDBRow, MDBCol } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';
import Movie from './movie';

const movieGrid = () => {

            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>

            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
            <MDBCol>
                <Movie />
            </MDBCol>
        </MDBRow>
    );
};

export default movieGrid;
